ZH: 请在学校区域内停止吸烟。
EN: Please refrain from smoking within the school premises.

ZH: 停止使用不受支持的软件。
EN: Stop using unsupported software.

ZH: 请听到广播后停止电梯内的活动。
EN: Please stop activities inside the elevator upon hearing the announcement.

ZH: 由于天气状况不好，航班被暂时停止。
EN: The flights have been temporarily suspended due to bad weather conditions.

ZH: 公共交通运营晚上十点停止。
EN: Public transportation services stop running at 10 PM.

ZH: 请停止你的车辆以便行人通过。
EN: Please stop your vehicle to allow pedestrians to cross.

ZH: 这个项目已经停止了五年。
EN: This project has been discontinued for five years.

ZH: 这个计划需要停止并重新评估。
EN: This plan needs to be stopped and reevaluated.

ZH: 他终于停止了犹豫，做出了决定。
EN: He finally stopped hesitating and made a decision.

ZH: 停止担心，一切都会好起来的。
EN: Stop worrying, everything will be alright.

ZH: 请停止你的工作一分钟默哀。
EN: Please stop your work for a minute of silence.

ZH: 他停止了哭泣，试图镇定下来。
EN: He stopped crying, trying to calm himself down.

ZH: 这个机器在损坏后会自动停止运行。
EN: This machine will automatically stop working after it is damaged.

ZH: 禁止停止车辆在这个区域。
EN: Stopping vehicles in this area is prohibited.

ZH: 警告：请停止未经授权的进入。
EN: Warning: Unauthorized entry is prohibited.

ZH: 停止攻击，并立即投降。
EN: Stop the attacks and surrender immediately.

ZH: 遇到红灯时，请停止你的车。
EN: Please stop your car when you encounter a red light.

ZH: 这个电子设备因电池耗尽而停止运行。
EN: This electronic device stopped working due to battery depletion.

ZH: 这台机器停止运行可能是由于故障。
EN: The machine might have stopped running due to a malfunction.

ZH: 停止和陌生人分享个人信息，以保护您的隐私。
EN: Stop sharing personal information with strangers to protect your privacy.
